/* 
  Animatronic Eye — Elegoo ESP32-WROOM-32
  State machine:
    HOMING    (0) → no face, eye parks at rest
    TRACKING  (1) → follows closest face
    STARTLED  (2) → white flash when face first appears
    SEARCHING (3) → sad wandering, natural eye colour breathing
    FORCED HOME   → capacitive touch toggles eye to home position

  Receives from Max (UDP port 8888):
    byte 0: 1   = tracking, pan/tilt in bytes 1 and 2
    byte 0: 255 = no face detected

  Servo 1 GPIO 18 = tilt (up/down)   MG996R
  Servo 2 GPIO 19 = pan  (left/right) MG996R
  Servo 3 GPIO 21 = homing            MG90S
  NeoPixel ring GPIO 5 (16 pixels)
  Capacitive touch GPIO 27 (T7) — touch to toggle home
*/

